Note: this repository contains code that independently replicates the
analysis methodology described in:

Shamsi, F., Piper, M., Ho, L.L. et al. Vascular smooth muscle-derived Trpv1+
progenitors are a source of cold-induced thermogenic adipocytes. Nat Metab 3,
485-495 (2021). https://doi.org/10.1038/s42255-021-00373-z

The MIT License above applies to the code in this repository. It does not
apply to the original paper's text/figures, or to the underlying dataset
(ArrayExpress E-MTAB-8564), which remain subject to their own respective
terms.
